Usage: hookmark [-b BASEDIR] [COMMAND]
  Store, edit and search bookmarks.

Available options:
  -v,--version             Show version
  -b BASEDIR               Base directory to store bookmarks in. Overwrites
                           $HOOKMARKHOME. Defaults to $HOME/.hookmarks
  -h,--help                Show this help text

Available commands:
  add                      Add bookmark
  show                     Show or search bookmark
  edit                     Edit bookmark
  rm                       Remove bookmark
  mv                       Move bookmark
  git                      Invoke git within hookmark directory
  version                  Show version
